================================================================================
Bundled font measurements
================================================================================

Glyph atlases (luminance ramps and shape vectors) ship as *measured coverage
numbers*, which are facts about character shapes, not copyrightable font
outlines. No font files are redistributed. Generate your own with
`xre glyphgen --font <file.ttf>`; prefer fonts whose license permits metric
extraction (e.g. JetBrains Mono, DejaVu, Fira Code).
